cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.RO 

The paper proposes a deep learning approach for stereo reconstruction, which is a computer vision task (cs.CV). The use of a deep network to enhance the reconstruction suggests that machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) are also likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions satellite images, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR) or robotics (cs.RO) depending on the context.
